 (field-induced\nPS). Moreover, a first-order SS-NO transition occurs between metastable phases\nand these metastable phases can exist inside the regions of the PS state\nstability. Such behaviour is associated with the presence of tricritical line\non the phase diagrams of the system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Dec 2014 10:26:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-09"}
