lusively to the small group of f-electron\nsuperconductors CeCoIn5, CeCu2Si2 and UPd2Al3, hidden order Kondo compounds\nCeB6 and URu2Si2 as well as the Kondo semiconductor YbB12 .\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Dec 2014 11:39:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Sep 2015 14:58:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-14"}
