ect and helix phase in spin-orbit coupled superconductors.\nIt also suggests an interesting method allowing to couple superconducting and\nmagnetic circuits.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Dec 2014 11:56:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 18 Nov 2015 08:55:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 2 Dec 2015 09:14:53 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 17 Dec 2015 09:12:35 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2016 13:37:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-02"}
