\circ}$). These results\nindicate that only a small number of $ORs$ are needed to describe isostructural\nRP heteroepitaxy and further demonstrate the potential of CSE in the design and\ngrowth of a wide range of complex functional oxides.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Dec 2014 15:05:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-24"}
