 for range-separated\ndensity-functional theory based on an exponential formula.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Dec 2014 15:41:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Feb 2015 17:21:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-20"}
